{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十五回「天峰大师」。楚留香与秃鹰约定三日后在莆田林家花园交付凶手，随即马不停蹄直奔莆田少林寺。为急见天峰大师，楚留香越墙而入，被四位灰袍少林僧人拦截。他以轻功周旋，声东击西佯装盗经，甩开追兵。途中遭遇灰眉监寺大师，硬挨一记百步神拳未伤，灰眉僧识破其身份，告知无花正为天峰大师烹茶。楚留香急中生智，以调虎离山之计闯入后院竹轩，大喝阻止天峰大师饮茶。在茶香竹影中，楚留香代烹新茶，借机向天峰大师询问天枫十四郎往事。天峰大师道出二十年前旧事：天枫十四郎东渡求战，先后与丐帮任老帮主和天峰大师交手；又讲述其与李琦姑娘的海外姻缘——李琦为黄山世家遗孤，东渡扶桑后与天枫十四郎结为夫妇，育有二子后不告而别。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅既然知道，不知可否赐知？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "我纵然说出那凶手是谁，你也无法可施，只不过……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "三天后，你可在莆田城里的林家花园等我，到时我自然会将杀死南宫灵的凶手交给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大师们用过饭了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_chang_seng",
      "speaker_name": "年长僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "二十年来，已从无江湖中人踏上少林寺的屋脊，施主今日既然破了例，想必绝非无故而来，但请将来意见示。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nian_chang_seng",
      "text": "在下的来意，纵然说了，大师们也不会相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主若不肯将来意相告，就莫怪贫僧等要无礼了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下生平最不愿和少林门下交手，大师们又何苦要逼我破例？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主若不愿动手，就随贫僧下去吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少林门下别的都好，就是火气太大了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_chang_seng",
      "speaker_name": "年长僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主好高明的轻功，难怪竟敢到少林寺中来撒野。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下并非撒野来的，等事情办完后，自当再来向大师们请罪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_chang_seng",
      "speaker_name": "年长僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄法传警应变，玄通、玄妙随我来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少林藏经，名重天下，大师们可以借给我瞧瞧么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人果然是为藏经而来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "留意藏经阁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主留步。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主如此武功，老僧从来未见，不知可否示知名姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "在下若是说出名姓，大师只怕便要以为在下是为盗经而来的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主若为盗经而来，便不会走来这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "在下楚留香。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "莫非是盗帅楚留香？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "大师远避红尘，不想竟也知道在下这见不得人的绰号。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老僧虽然久疏江湖侠踪，但却有个交游广阔的师侄，每当他来到此间，总会为老僧述说些新奇有趣的故事，而楚香帅的豪情壮举，正是所有的事件中最有趣，最能动人心魄的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "大师说的，莫非是无花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "数百年来，少林门下若论交游广阔的弟子，也不过只有他一个人而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "他……他此刻是否已在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主此来，莫非就是找他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "在下此来，主要还为的是想拜见天峰大师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "掌门师兄虽已久避外客，但楚施主这样的人，他想必还是乐于接见的，只可惜施主此刻来的甚是不巧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "莫非天峰大师已……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "掌门师兄万念皆空，惟有茶之一癖，始终未改，他此刻正在品茶，那是谁也打扰不得的。",
      "tone": "含笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "天峰大师若是独自品茶，在下也就不着急了，只要能先见着无花师兄，也是一样的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主此刻既然见不着掌门师兄，便也见不着无花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "少林门下，精于东瀛茶道的，也惟有无花一人，只要他来到此间，第一件事便是为掌门师兄汲水烹茶。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "无花此刻正在为天峰大师烹茶么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚施主想见他们，恐怕只好等到明晨了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "他们品茶之处，莫非便是后院？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "text": "但大师身后来的，岂非就是无花？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_mei_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰眉僧",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "这茶喝不得的！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主如此闯来，不觉太鲁莽了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "在下一时情急，望大师恕罪。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "二十年来，能一路闯入老僧禅房中的，施主还是第一人，既能来此，自然不俗，先请坐下待茶如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，楚兄既然来了，何不坐下来喝杯茶，以涤俗尘。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "原来是楚施主，难怪轻功之高，天下已不作第二人想了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "不敢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老僧虽然久绝世事，但能见到当世俊杰之丰采，心里还是欢喜得很，寒寺无酒，楚施主何妨以茶作酒。",
      "tone": "含笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "这茶喝不得的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此茶纵非仙种，亦属妙品，怎会喝不得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "在下受人所托，已为大师带来了绝妙新茶，而且在下自信对于烹茶一道，也颇不俗，大师难道不想先尝一尝么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，老僧就叨扰了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不想楚兄竟也有此雅兴，妙极妙极。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "如此珍贵的水，倒了不可惜么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此水乃初雪所溶，虽也珍贵，寺中窖存却有不少，楚兄若有此嗜，不妨带一瓶回去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此刻水尚未煮沸，楚施主正好将来意说出，面对名茶，正是老僧心情好时，楚施主若是有事相询，也在此时问出为佳。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "晚辈此来，只是想求大师说个故事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "故事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "十余年前，有位扶桑武士天枫十四郎，渡海东来，曾与两位中土高手较量过武功，其中一位是丐帮任老帮主，还有一位，不知是否大师？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "二十年前的往事，老僧都已几乎忘怀了，不想施主今日竟又重提此事……不错，施主说的，正是老僧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "天枫十四郎东渡求战，却无求胜之心，反似抱有必死之念，若是晚辈猜的不错，他莫非有什么伤心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你猜得不错，他的确有些伤心的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "大师若肯示知，晚辈感激不尽。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "往事如云烟，老僧本已不愿提起，但施主你不远千里而来，为的只是问此事，其中关系，必定极大。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "大师明察秋毫，晚辈也不敢隐瞒，此事关系的确极大，但晚辈却可保证，晚辈相询此事，绝无丝毫私心恶意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "施主若有私心恶意，又岂能坐在此地。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "大师明鉴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "天枫十四郎坚忍卓绝，嗜武成痴，却不幸又是个多情种子，二十多年前，华山与黄山世家两大剑派发生惨斗，血战连绵多年，黄山世家终致惨败，到后来战到只剩下李琦一人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "此事与天枫十四郎有何关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "李琦姑娘为了避祸，便搭乘了海上商船，东渡扶桑，那时她已受了内伤，再加上海路艰难，到了扶桑岛上，已是不良于行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "难道这位姑娘竟遇着了天枫十四郎不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正是如此，天枫十四郎暗对这李姑娘一见钟情，几日不眠不休，治澈了李姑娘的伤势，李姑娘自也难免被他真诚所动，就在她伤势痊澈的第四天，就和天枫十四郎结成了夫妇。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "text": "良缘天定，结于海外，倒当真是段佳话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "天峰大师",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜他们幸福的日子并不长，李姑娘为天枫十四郎生了两个孩子后，竟又忽然不告而别，只留下封书信。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    }
  ],
